                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 left-border">
                    <div class="bottom-border">
                        <h1 class="heading2">Upcoming Contests</h1>
                        <a href="" id="ac1" target="_blank"><h3 id="c1">Contest 1</h3></a>
                        <h4 id="Time1" class="time">Time 1</h4>
